00:11:46.310 --> 00:11:48.100
Nobody says anything
or does anything.

00:11:48.100 --> 00:11:49.400
There's no oversight.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:53.620
The state doesn't come out and
say, you've got to clean this up.

00:11:53.620 --> 00:11:55.720
It's left to the people
who are living there.

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:58.620
&gt;&gt; The first thing that happens
