is the loan, and then there's a pump

00:12:20.070 --> 00:12:23.680
which serves as your diaphragm,
which pumps the air out,

00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:27.500
creating negative pressure,
opening the bag and bringing in air

00:12:27.500 --> 00:12:30.170
so it can be sealed and
sent to the lab for testing.

00:12:30.170 --> 00:12:33.780
And they process it immediately.

00:12:33.780 --> 00:12:36.740
&gt;&gt; Bucket brigade techniques
