00:21:32.240 --> 00:21:35.710
But it's using the tools of
science, it's generating data

00:21:35.710 --> 00:21:40.410
from the environment, analyzing
it, collaborating with scientists,

00:21:40.410 --> 00:21:43.050
and then delivering back
solutions that work.

00:21:43.050 --> 00:21:46.990
So citizens plus sensors
working for solutions,

00:21:46.990 --> 00:21:49.610
that's a pretty good summary of
what today's citizen science is.

